OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand sunny to end the week. Light winds
OL,7,Fon Thursday, though breezier on Friday
OL,8,Fand Saturday. Hot throughout as
OL,9,Ftemperatures increase.
